          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": "",
          "data": {
            "html": "<p>The Aya Circle of Care program at Taibu was developed for the community to provide focused, individualized care and support to those of African/Caribbean or Black descent living with HIV.</p><p>\"We believe in the strength of our community and we are committed to serving you with respect and dignity\".</p><p>Let's see what services The AYA circle provides!</p>",
